                <head>167. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>On March 23, the National Advisory Council on International Monetary and
                    Financial Problems discussed the Department of State proposal to eliminate the
                    maintenance-of-value requirement on U.S. loans of local currency. The minutes of
                    that portion of the meeting are printed as <ref target="#d45">Document
                    45</ref>.</p>
            </div>
